query: WITH entities AS (SELECT authentication_id, id FROM core_users WHERE ((authentication_id IS NOT DISTINCT FROM $3) AND COALESCE(id > $2, true) OR COALESCE(authentication_id > $3, authentication_id IS NOT NULL)) ORDER BY authentication_id ASC NULLS FIRST, id ASC LIMIT $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: Repo__Id", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN core_user_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.authentication_id asc nulls first, i.id asc, i.id, e.sequence
